column5: Just came in and it was warm and clamy.Sit, click on OFC and out of nowhere comes these high winds and black clouds. I hate it when it does that.Seen a few people running and thought maybe something was happening,so I grab the camera. As you can see over the bay,it looked like something was going to transpier. Everytime I see clouds starting to drop and form little V,s,always think it could be a tornado.    <embed width="600" height="361" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowFullscreen="true" allowNetworking="all" wmode="transparent" src="http://static.photobucket.com/player.swf" flashvars="file=http%3A%2F%2Fvidmg.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fv731%2Fmisfish%2F20100628_01.mp4">
I just came in from flying bud... landed just as it blew threw here. Torrental rain..lost 1/2 my friggin laneway gravel again !
Holy cow!Headed out to a local spot for a few casts after hitting lpb, and I thought it was going to hit hard.The fest started up the fireworks in daylight.
I kept snappin pics,i just got the in betweens,these were the best ones.
